722040f-c.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 33rd Street
722040f-c.text:

Park Avenue at 34th Street, looking northwest from One Park Avenue
building at 33ro Street. In the left foreground is shown the
north wing of tho Vanderbilt Hotel, and in the right foreground
the tower of the Seventy-First Regiment Armory.
Down on the N.w. corner of 34th Street the Community Church (1867)
is being demolished to make room for an apartment house.
February 27, 1931.
